@b{BashStyle-NG} contains a Custom Prompt Builder that allows you to create a
prompt from scratch, or modify one the existing prompt styles shipped with
@b{BasShtyle-NG}.

You can insert symbolic colors into your prompt, which will allow you to change
the colors right from the Styles Settings.

The Toolbox allows you to insert informations into your prompt, both Bash default
and @b{BashStyle-NG} specific functions.

@defvr {Setting} use_custom_prompt
@end defvr

